{"_id":"6a177b3fbcf1fb2fc412dc44","referenceId":"d4d71eb1-44dd-4fb0-8653-dd515399e80c","order":7,"text":"# How can I lower the cost of car insurance?\nThere's plenty you can do to reduce the cost of car insurance. For example, you might choose to pay annually instead of monthly, so you don't need to pay interest.As for reducing your car insurance quote, can you improve the car's security by keeping it on a driveway or in a garage instead of on the street?\nMake sure that your annual mileage estimate is as accurate as possible. Adding extra miles 'just in case' can bump up your policy price. Plus, if your mileage changes during the year, you can update it in your online account.\nIt's important to make sure you're fully covered for everything you need, so make sure to list the most up-to-date and accurate information on your quote.","disabled":false,"data":{"firstPage":"1","lastPage":"2"},"embedding":{"vector":[0.038543701171875,0.007568359375,0.0168609619140625,0.060546875,-0.005954742431640625,-0.01097869873046875,-0.0313720703125,0.049591064453125,0.00873565673828125,0.0223846435546875,-0.007411956787109375,-0.0021457672119140625,-0.036712646484375,0.03070068359375,0.0295867919921875,-0.0254364013671875,-0.00983428955078125,0.047393798828125,0.0001246929168701172,0.0149078369140625,-0.0010976791381835938,0.0333251953125,-0.014801025390625,-0.004192352294921875,0.00917816162109375,0.00424957275390625,-0.00904083251953125,-0.00618743896484375,0.0236358642578125,-0.0291748046875,0.03424072265625,-0.002651214599609375,-0.0001665353775024414,0.033599853515625,-0.005008697509765625,0.0248870849609375,-0.00931549072265625,-0.059478759765625,0.04376220703125,-0.0787353515625,-0.02734375,0.043548583984375,0.03289794921875,-0.0063629150390625,-0.0019359588623046875,0.02349853515625,0.0592041015625,-0.0380859375,-0.035308837890625,0.0033130645751953125,-0.039764404296875,-0.025665283203125,-0.0198974609375,-0.0065765380859375,0.01407623291015625,0.0233154296875,-0.0165252685